English: Hello, I am from Chokwe, a tribal group in Peru. I am a photographer and I have been to Machu Picchu many times. I have taken many photos of the ruins.

text: Enceladus cilyi Cuma cayemuka cumumulalyi watangwa, canatemuka wundji wa 90% ca kutemuka nhi mwalwa wuze akutambula.
translated_text: Chokwe: Enceladus cilyi Cuma cayemuka cumumulalyi watangwa, canatemuka wundji wa 90% ca kutemuka nhi mwalwa wuze akutambula. English: Enceladus is currently the hottest place in the solar system, with a temperature of about 1,200 degrees Celsius.

text: Nhicimwe mucihasa kusoloka shina mwilu munazuluka nhi mupema handji milundu yindji yinatujingilyika. Cimwe cihanda cacifuci cino mucihasa kusoloka handji kwiva mukaci kacisapwe.
translated_text: Chokwe: Nhicimwe mucihasa kusoloka shina mwilu munazuluka nhi mupema handji milundu yindji yinatujingilyika. text: Mussono kali Japao, Japao te kali imue ilha kutala ngue Gra-Bretanha.

text: Apia ili capital iya Samoa, mbongue ili mu ilha iya Upolonhiili amue athu iya kakumi mukehe mwixi iya 40.000 habitantes.
translated_text: Chokwe: Apia ili capital iya Samoa, mbongue ili mu ilha iya Upolonhiili amue athu iya kakumi mukehe mwixi iya 40.000 habitantes. English: Apia, capital of Samoa, the largest city in the island of Upolu.

text: Ili ikehe cindji ali Maria nhi inene cindji hali ihela issuko.
translated_text: Chokwe: Ili ikehe cindji ali Maria nhi inene cindji hali ihela issuko. English: The angel said to her, “Don’t be afraid, Mary. You have found favor with God.”

text: Katalilo wa linhica lia cifuci cesue, ha milimoyakutalatala shimbu, ya ifuci yalicinga, kasoluelenhiumwe linhika kuyslândia ha phoso ya kunhima.
translated_text: Chokwe: Katalilo wa linhica lia cifuci cesue, ha milimoyakutalatala shimbu, ya ifuci yalicinga, kasoluelenhiumwe linhika kuyslândia ha phoso ya kunhima. English: The first thing I noticed about the Chokwe language was that it was very similar to the Luapula language. I was surprised to find that the Chokwe language was a member of the Luapula language family. I was also surprised to find that the Chokwe language was spoken by a people who were not from the Luapula language family.

text: Kanahwimina kusongo lya mulundu kucivumbuko ca Meca, thanda yahululu kushi nawa nhiwume muthu wa kucifuci cekha.
translated_text: Chokwe: Kanahwimina kusongo lya mulundu kucivumbuko ca Meca, thanda yahululu kushi nawa nhiwume muthu wa kucifuci cekha. English: The Chokwe people are the descendants of the ancient people of the Chokwe Kingdom. They are the people of the Chokwe Kingdom.
